<h3 id="add_margin">Add Margin to your account.</h3>

```python
breeze.add_margin(product_type="margin", 
                    stock_code="ICIBAN", 
                    exchange_code="BSE", 
                    settlement_id="2021220", 
                    add_amount="100", 
                    margin_amount="3817.10", 
                    open_quantity="10", 
                    cover_quantity="0", 
                    category_index_per_stock="", 
                    expiry_date="", 
                    right="", 
                    contract_tag="", 
                    strike_price="", 
                    segment_code="")
```

